Ing '''Hayward''' ({{pron-en|ˈheɪwərd}}; dati, '''Haywards''', '''Haywards Station''', ampong '''Haywood''') metung yang lakanbalen king [[East Bay (California)|East Bay]] king [[Alameda County, California|Alameda County]]. Ing Hayward iya ing panganam yang pekamaragul diling lakanbalen keng [[San Francisco Bay Area]] at atiu keng aslagan dake ning pampang ning Bay, pilatan ning [[San Leandro]] ampo nign [[Union City]], keng aslagan danggut ning [[Tete San Mateo]]. Agpang inyang 2000 census, ing populasiun ning lakanbalen 140,030 ya . Ing tantiang poplasiun inyang 2007, 155,312 ya.













